headline: Wells Fargo Maintains Equal-Weight on Humana, Lowers Price Target to $206
summary: Wells Fargo  analyst Stephen Baxter   maintains Humana (NYSE:HUM) with a Equal-Weight and lowers the price target from $290 to $206.

headline: Humana Commits Over $1.7M Throughout Illinois To Modernize Housing, Support Workforce Deployment
summary: Humana Inc. (NYSE:HUM) has committed more than $1.7 million in strategic investments to support housing stability and workforce development, reduce disparities, and expand access to maternal and behavioral healthcare
